import React from 'react'
import {Typography,AppBar,Button,ButtonGroup,Card,CardContent,CardMedia,CssBaseline,Grid,Toolbar,Container, CardActions} from '@material-ui/core'


const OfferScreen = () => {
    return (
        <>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">
          Sign up
       </Button>
           <Button variant="contained" color="inherit">
         Login
         </Button>
        </>
    )
}

export default OfferScreen
